{
  "id": "RAW_699476d2",
  "title": "OpenAI 刚融到 1220 亿美元，却在二级市场「没人接盘」？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651025305&idx=2&sn=c5a862e1fbb69835bc4d14665ca22586",
  "date": "2026-04-02 03:47:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d86eafdd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2F5L8bhP5dIqHubJmHTGibicVDCHYOfwcTaDQEGI4SsLCicYQvnB6nuD1YkqAsLSZ6NaoicRcxZG14rznH2JW2bGyjMxYW7EqoW4QmyMWGv3Iic6cw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p>不是不看好，而是先等等。</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.04259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503523662\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=97ed75af&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicoCrHPEpT0tQiceNphESCa2eJTqstP8G0yqMTkeMFrOGue6kOyCKdTkA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">机器之心编辑部</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">据彭博社报道，OpenAI 的股票在二级市场上正在「失宠」。随着投资者迅速将资金转向其主要竞争对手 Anthropic，OpenAI 的部分股票在二级市场甚至变得难以出售。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"750\" data-imgfileid=\"503541633\" data-ratio=\"1.0190217391304348\" data-width=\"736\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"736\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c61f0f01&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqGTnDUib6Wn3fHkhWAIw2u7Oq92Wg47zciaCKRZfrBtYricedHTcotxs2hWgibrmEYEFtNPef7ice88WYDUzicWNxRttQII84FY9JrYU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"2\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Next Round Capital 创始人 Ken Smythe 提到，尽管公司刚刚完成大规模融资，但近期市场对其股票的兴趣有所回落。过去几周，大约有六家机构尝试出售总计约 6 亿美元的 OpenAI 股份，但暂未找到合适买家；而另一边，市场上已有约 20 亿美元资金在等待进入 Anthropic。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"3\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">从交易平台的数据来看，这种分化也有所体现。Augment 和 Hiive 等平台显示，Anthropic 的需求更为活跃。Augment 联合创始人 Adam Crawley 指出，目前 OpenAI 的估值约为 8520 亿美元，Anthropic 为 3800 亿美元，价差本身就让一部分投资者更倾向于后者——毕竟在估值尚未「走高之前」入场，想象空间更大一些。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"3\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6526207605344296\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"973\" data-width=\"973\" data-height=\"635\" data-imgfileid=\"503541634\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=119e8d5f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHAby5rqKWjBhia8jYTLpQw10Uhc4KQ13PpVR9xZ2m8YeMgfAx6S6jLWArw3z0weicelYy6zXnyKZcucJ5oZt7jh95W40tJTmmTU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"4\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">报价层面，这种情绪也有反映：OpenAI 的买方报价对应估值约为 7650 亿美元，相比其融资估值存在约 10% 的折价；而 Anthropic 的买方报价则对应约 6000 亿美元，较上一轮融资溢价超过 50%。简单来说，一个在「打折出让」，一个在「溢价排队」。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"5\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不过，把视角拉回一级市场，画风又完全不同。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"6\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">就在本周，</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&amp;mid=2651024900&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c03ebf248ebe66571260d9d9adf19217&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"OpenAI 刚刚完成新一轮融资\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">OpenAI 刚刚完成新一轮融资</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，获得高达 1220 亿美元的承诺资本，投后估值达到 8520 亿美元。参与方包括亚马逊、英伟达、软银，以及微软、Andreessen Horowitz 等一线机构。与此同时，OpenAI 也首次向个人投资者开放渠道，通过银行募集了超过 30 亿美元，并进入 ARK Invest 部分 ETF。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"7\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在机制上，公司还尝试降低个人投资者参与门槛，比如推出零费用通道，并提醒市场警惕通过 SPV 间接持股的高费用结构。相比之下，市场上针对 Anthropic 的类似交易，仍普遍收取 15% - 20% 的附带权益费用。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"8\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">从基本面来看，OpenAI 的增长依然强劲：当前月营收约 20 亿美元，预计 2025 年全年收入将达到 131 亿美元；ChatGPT 周活跃用户超过 9 亿，付费用户超过 5000 万，企业收入占比超过 40%。不过，高昂的算力和人力投入也意味着公司仍未实现盈利。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"9\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为控制成本，OpenAI 近期也在做一些「收紧动作」，包括暂停部分产品（如&nbsp;</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&amp;mid=2651023578&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=d4822b55bc70dc39cb6fb0cc3f0967fd&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"Sora\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Sora</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">）。在产品路径上，公司正在将 ChatGPT、Codex 与智能体能力整合，试图构建一个更统一的「AI 超级应用」。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"10\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">相比之下，一些投资者对 Anthropic 的印象则更偏向「稳健型选手」：基础设施投入相对克制，在高利润率的企业市场表现稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"11\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当然，Anthropic 也并非没有波动。近期其被美国国防部列入供应链风险名单，并因此提起诉讼；同时，</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&amp;mid=2651024890&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ef03a969ea07774bbe6935c89a1370e2&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"一次 npm 包更新中意外泄露约 51.2 万行 Claude Code 源代码\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一次 npm 包更新中意外泄露约 51.2 万行 Claude Code 源代码</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，也引发了对其安全流程的讨论。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"12\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前，两家公司均在考量上市计划，OpenAI 的 IPO 进程预计最早于今年启动。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"13\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">社区方面，有观点认为，同一天既能完成 1220 亿美元融资，又被说成「失宠」，本身就有些矛盾；也有人怀疑，这种说法可能忽略了时间滞后或市场结构差异。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2880658436213992\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"729\" data-width=\"729\" data-height=\"210\" data-imgfileid=\"503541635\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5c727bb6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEl92B04iaOrvk7Z4TaeOpVorarfQfaayHHUalUn4mHIEfJoNgXvOCk0CM1eFDf2S3UEoxLzBWnfJl28HEibGOhWezxfymuquqxw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.388283378746594\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"734\" data-width=\"734\" data-height=\"285\" data-imgfileid=\"503541636\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f82ef5c5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqFMfqXAibVxqaIvBiahE9pLO00ltGMWjv2Q7wicbRviahpsDoibcV2jXaBmKLTTficdoKEJXHKu3HTjaNAibIsPTksibL0XJw6ZM3R5MDY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"14\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">另一类更偏市场视角的解释则更「冷静」：如果 OpenAI 的 IPO 已有明确时间预期（例如 2026 年），那么理性的投资者自然会减少在二级市场以高溢价买入的动力，转而等待公开市场直接参与。相比之下，Anthropic 尚未给出清晰的上市路径，二级市场几乎是唯一入口，需求自然更集中。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3082191780821918\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"730\" data-width=\"730\" data-height=\"225\" data-imgfileid=\"503541637\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1e84265d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqG3MIIyXNBGnKla4AuoibymTLib4OHTTZhOIwcWKDBLr92qKLRhhlP82EQDQPUEwcibqfanQAQrq9ZyUXB6qxe8icF92Q63FjF9UZk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3844049247606019\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"731\" data-width=\"731\" data-height=\"281\" data-imgfileid=\"503541638\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f06b59f9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEsl1ib46eXYV40tos9lLjBxBaczjqWJCA8QicT08ibjewP1xlDBUXC3T5cuntcu5jJpmeCJ9Z8MGybQnVyb82r3GeokZ8pN7co80%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9918367346938776\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"735\" data-width=\"735\" data-height=\"729\" data-imgfileid=\"503541639\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4b6aa8c3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEtr0wcv9XpUuA52o6c8YWO5PzRP25ZhbysWqpysUIJDrwRc1ZHickrXVlCbJUnL03nPvzw9yKZJbXNXuaaKJjgH8tosVpynpDg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"15\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">换句话说，这种「冷热不均」，也可能只是资本在不同阶段的正常流动。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"16\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而在 AI 这个行业里，还有一个变量始终存在：节奏。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-path-to-node=\"17\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">今天的市场偏好，并不意味着明天的格局。只要有一次足够重磅的产品更新，叙事很可能就会重新改写。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.41689373297002724\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"734\" data-width=\"734\" data-height=\"306\" data-imgfileid=\"503541640\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7898a793&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqE1HT3kE2gajDRMvTgFDZypnJ87PkKdSlQGs26kMCtakicvH95r5l74Xztkm2lpXY5MFWm4meT0ur0lCVPYFfhc5v7C5tT7RnLk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(34, 34, 34);margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-size-adjust:auto;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgb(34, 34, 34);margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-size-adjust:auto;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/openai-demand-sinks-on-secondary-market-as-anthropic-runs-hot\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-01/openai-demand-sinks-on-secondary-market-as-anthropic-runs-hot</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文报道了 OpenAI 在一级市场完成巨额融资的同时，二级市场却出现需求降温，而竞争对手 Anthropic 则因估值空间和 IPO 预期差异成为投资者新宠。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文报道了 OpenAI 在一级市场完成巨额融资的同时，二级市场却出现需求降温，而竞争对手 Anthropic 则因估值空间和 IPO 预期差异成为投资者新宠。",
  "summary": "文章深入分析了 OpenAI 与 Anthropic 在二级市场表现的显著分化。尽管 OpenAI 近期刚完成 1220 亿美元的巨额融资，投后估值高达 8520 亿美元，但在二级市场却面临约 6 亿美元股份待售且买家寥寥的局面，买方报价甚至出现 10% 的折价。与之形成鲜明对比的是，Anthropic 在二级市场需求火爆，买方报价溢价超 50%。这种「冷热不均」主要源于：OpenAI 估值已处于高位且 IPO 预期明确，导致投资者倾向于等待公开市场；而 Anthropic 估值相对较低且二级市场是稀缺入口。此外，文章还对比了两者的基本面，指出 OpenAI 虽营收强劲但成本高昂，正通过整合智能体能力寻求突破。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "OpenAI 一二级市场表现出现显著背离。",
      "explanation": "一级市场虽获 1220 亿美元巨额注资，但二级市场因估值过高及买家转向 Anthropic 而出现流动性压力，甚至出现折价转让现象。"
    },
    {
      "point": "投资者对 Anthropic 的兴趣在二级市场反超 OpenAI。",
      "explanation": "Anthropic 被视为更稳健的选手，且因估值相对较低（3800 亿 vs 8520 亿），二级市场买方报价较融资估值溢价超 50%。"
    },
    {
      "point": "IPO 预期和市场结构差异是导致分化的核心原因。",
      "explanation": "OpenAI 明确的 IPO 计划让投资者更愿等待公开市场，而 Anthropic 缺乏清晰上市路径，使二级市场成为目前唯一的入场渠道。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "OpenAI 的买方报价对应估值约为 7650 亿美元，相比其融资估值存在约 10% 的折价；而 Anthropic 的买方报价则对应约 6000 亿美元，较上一轮融资溢价超过 50%。",
    "如果 OpenAI 的 IPO 已有明确时间预期，那么理性的投资者自然会减少在二级市场以高溢价买入的动力，转而等待公开市场直接参与。",
    "今天的市场偏好，并不意味着明天的格局。只要有一次足够重磅的产品更新，叙事很可能就会重新改写。"
